013present}}\n{{s-inc}}\n|-\n{{s-prec|usa}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Mike Crapo]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Seniority in the United States Senate|United States Senators by seniority]]|years=16th}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Debbie Stabenow]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{Current Delaware statewide political officials}}\n{{DE-FedRep}}\n{{Current U.S. Senators}}\n{{USSenChairs}}\n{{SenHomelandSecurityCommitteeChairmen}}\n{{USSenDE}}\n{{USRepDE}}\n{{Governors of Delaware}}\n{{USCongRep-start|congresses= 98th\u2013102nd, 107th-present [[United States Congress]]es |state=[[Delaware]]}}\n{{USCongRep/DE/98}}\n{{USCongRep/DE/99}}\n{{USCongRep/DE/100}}\n{{USCongRep/DE/101}}\n{{USCongRep/DE/102}}\n{{USCongRep/DE/107}}\n{{USCongRep/DE/108}}\n{{USCongRep/DE/109}}\n{{USCongRep/DE/110}}\n{{USCongRep/DE/111}}\n{{USCongRep/DE/112}}\n{{USCongRep/DE/113}}\n{{USCongRep/DE/114}}\n{{USCongRep/DE/115}}\n{{USCongRep/DE/116}}\n{{USCongRep-end}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Carper, Thomas R.}}\n[[Category:1947 births]]\n[[Category:21st-century American politicians]]\n[[Category:American naval personnel of the Vietnam War]]\n[[Category:American Presbyterians]]\n[[Category:Businesspeople from Delaware]]\n[[Category:Delaware Democrats]]\n[[Category:Democratic Party members of the United States House of Representatives]]\n[[Category:Democratic Party state governors of the United States]]\n[[Category:Democratic Party United States senators]]\n[[Category:Governors of Delaware]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Members of the United States House of Representatives from Delaware]]\n[[Category:Military personnel from West Virginia]]\n[[Category:Ohio State University alumni]]\n[[Category:People from Beckley, West Virginia]]\n[[Category:People from Wilmington, Delaware]]\n[[Category:State treasurers of Delaware]]\n[[Category:United States Navy captains]]\n[[Category:United States Navy reservists]]\n[[Category:United States senators from Delaware]]\n[[Category:University of Delaware alumni]]\n[[Category:Whetstone High S